00:49:51.320 --> 00:49:55.880
[Unknown]: a roundtable of other IBM hosts like Varun Duggirala of Advertising Instead, Naren Chinoy

00:49:55.880 --> 00:50:01.200
[Unknown]: from Simplified, Dinkar Divedi from Geekfruit, and of course me and Abbas.

